column2: "I don't know what you... I don't remember anything... I don't know the name Yucreta..."
"If you don't want me to kill him... Shoot me, shoot!"

"If I were a Dark Falz,
then I will disappear with this attack..."

"Because of that, the end.
It should end like this..."
"I am not... a Dark Falz. I was never a Dark Falz..."
"Ahh that hurt... I know I told you to shoot, but I didn't think you would, Partner."
"Shut up...! Don't call me by that name!"
"I don't remember anything... Your name, my name, everything..."
"I have nothing anymore... I'm neither Dark Falz nor ARKS. I... How do I..."
